{"tid":1175733,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[半鐵膠][多圖少字]12日九洲關東西初嘗頭等喪食拉麵之旅","createTime":"2019-05-28T18:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T03:51:44.000Z","uid":31626,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"864453aed339fa120e557fb4b8f465db69469d6e","tid":1175733,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T18:00:35.000Z","msg":"前幾日先返到嚟 忙到趴街 結果而家先有時間打呢篇遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />文筆拙劣 盡量以圖代字 多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攝影設備: GALAXY S10+ (Google Camera)<br />\n旅遊日期:13/5/2019~24/5/2019<br />\n旅遊行程:<br />\nDAY1:HKG-KOJ 初嘗吉列黑毛豬扒飯 半日櫻島遊<br />\nDAY2:指宿玉手箱 西大山 枕崎 去熊本<br />\nDAY3:熊本市一日遊 三餐拉麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDAY4:由布院之森 金麟湖 由布院一日遊<br />\nDAY5:SL人吉 鰻魚飯 人吉城 翡翠山翡翠<br />\nDAY6:FUK&gt;HND 初嚐JAL國內線頭等艙 去東京會合朋友 秋葉原週邊鳩行<br />\nDAY7:去一之關坐 POKEMON WITH YOU列車 來回氣仙沼 夜晚去原宿陪朋友食鰻魚<br />\nDAY8:朝早ANA見學 中午坐超景踴子去橫浜 下午再去JAL見學 夜晚台場<br />\nDAY9:朝早敗走飯田商店 再去大阪 通天閣 初訪無鐵砲拉麵<br />\nDAY10:朝早大阪&gt;博多 尋找失去的電話之行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 米奇老味800系 下午返去祇園 花見小路 八阪神社 夜晚返梅田食燒肉放題 再行5.8公里返酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDAY11:遠征箕島 食 和dining清乃 下午再去稻荷大社 千本鳥居 夜晚再一次敗走人類麵類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心齋橋<br />\nDAY12:朝早去中津食 麥與麵助當午餐 再去奈良比鹿撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夜晚KIX-HKG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be93b7d94b02867b01d1c4fd4249f301d4ca4592","tid":1175733,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T18:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fd1d4a7e6b409f27db60ca45a34bc6e0bff0e4","tid":1175733,"uid":145839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T18:13:35.000Z","msg":"留名 btw有西大山冇稚內既 攪錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e245a275a5177758165cf7e5aa3c0480d74c3fb3","tid":1175733,"uid":145839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T18:19:52.000Z","msg":"國內線 頭等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾錢程"},{"pid":"5bd4827a346efdaa16308d32e1b401cd974214df","tid":1175733,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T18:24:01.000Z","msg":"DAY1:HKG-KOJ<br />\n香港直航KOJ得兩班機:廚叉同老母<br />\n咁老母個時間比較上好些少 惟有揀佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n晨咁早坐N車入機場T2 CHECK-IN <br />\n空無一人嘅老母COUNTER <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxmQOKT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxmQOKT.jpg&h=561f84e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n放行李爽手淨腳 光速出飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4865CEZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4865CEZ.jpg&h=3df9206a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我想舒服些少 買飛嗰陣揀埋U-BIZ 貪佢行李座位一次過包曬 整埋LOUNGE比你 舒舒服服 食飽再坐UO苦行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當初仲以為係PLAZA公廁LOUNGE 點知原來轉咗做廚叉紫荊堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要唔係開24HRS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQ1AZTT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQ1AZTT.jpg&h=3becf468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LiGVse.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LiGVse.jpg&h=8e3a6ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早餐主要得中式食物 叉包炒麵皮蛋粥 外加茄汁豆放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另外可以同staff落單嗌份太陽蛋 雜菜通粉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BoFRydV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBoFRydV.jpg&h=bbfc7aa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2n4TdX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2n4TdX.jpg&h=9f1dc119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食飽沖完涼先上機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> BTW沖涼房得一間 喺廁所入面 所以班機趕時間嘅話 盡早問COUNTER拎牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DAuOAsg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDAuOAsg.jpg&h=f691a5fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sr9u4kD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsr9u4kD.jpg&h=0d14e881&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8a6af762605a189e83bd4ccea5906d7ac90b782","tid":1175733,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e245a275a5177758165cf7e5aa3c0480d74c3fb3","tid":1175733,"uid":145839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T18:19:52.000Z","msg":"國內線 頭等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾錢程"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T18:24:30.000Z","msg":"JAL EXPLORER PASS+8000JPY"},{"pid":"bc723f1f360aac321a1aad4ad200d73d6e0a88f8","tid":1175733,"uid":38195,"