ss=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3znE5p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3znE5p.jpg&h=7aa71c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n13A 緊急出口位 不過椅背有得唉後 加埋特闊long腳位 爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0TAidn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0TAidn6.jpg&h=b80b5a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾耐冇抹玻璃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06P3puN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06P3puN.jpg&h=a46d6652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講起上面呢三個出風口，點解之後啲A330 A350唔再用番？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k84iXPO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk84iXPO.jpg&h=dfbbcc13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n表定0730 但係成0800先起飛 應該關班機FULL爆事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHm9j29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHm9j29.jpg&h=03143b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7v6ngv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7v6ngv.jpg&h=2c7eba6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d296adcc84567ed2ecd3850d94949d4f08b9b318","tid":1175733,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T19:56:14.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n聽日再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbc739b5c662ac265d3471940bc71c533abd692","tid":1175733,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:26:23.000Z","msg