！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VLH4Ycq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVLH4Ycq.jpg&h=438964de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"381e965e6b0b256638ba10ec468e4e9f0f007d66","tid":1175733,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T09:38:58.000Z","msg":"鹿兒島嘅第一餐 川久<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xg1tFzV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxg1tFzV.jpg&h=5b1f5a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oco0wGB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foco0wGB.jpg&h=8bbcb44d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUGYimC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUGYimC.jpg&h=c8cf24ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zt5RDmD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZt5RDmD.jpg&h=e13d9b03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JwViimE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwViimE.jpg&h=18cb31ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gvD4dU1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgvD4dU1.jpg&h=a4c775a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n碟豬軟骨夠曬淋 夠曬入味<br />\n而塊吉列黑豚豬柳就唔洗多講 超juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37daa1d27da3c1f58d0db653b24194528bf1407f","tid":1175733,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434bb772efa8b80af5169b35409adfca8d6c6881","tid":1175733,"uid":114754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T13:13:39.000Z","msg":"lm等更新"},{"pid":"2cf920c61933d325efbca411de